Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:41.61,Ending ext,Ending,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,46)}ANYWAY KOKORO NO BEKUTORU SO MANY REASON HANASHITERU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:46.19,Ending ext,Ending,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,33)}JIYOU NI SORA WO TOBITAI KEREDO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:51.07,Ending ext,Ending,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,33)}HANE WO HIROGERU BASHO GA NAI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:57.79,Ending ext,Ending,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,33)}DEMO SHINJITERU KATACHI NO NAI MIRAI GA ARU YO
